reviews.review_text:
Pleasant two-day surprise This second night of two at UofM is a little diamond in the rough - well-played, energetic first set where all the boys are ON and clearly having fun. 
Just finished listening to the second set - this show was really good in all respects. I didn't get any bring down the house moments from it but it was all I'd ask for in a show if I was there. 
The recording itself is excellent - crisper than that posted for the night before (also a tasty surprise of a show) and well mixed. One of the things that knocks a show down for me the is inability to hear Phil booming through; this mix has him coming in clear but not overly loud. Same guys recorded and transferred so I'm not clear on the difference, I just like this sound a little better than the night before. Note - tracks are all mislabeled after Masterpiece but easy enough to follow. Very enjoyable and highly recommended as is the previous night. Peace
